I’m in Ravenclaw and a bit shy when you first meet me, but funny and sarcastic after. I love reading and acting, which sounds ironic considering I am shy, but somehow works. My Result: HUFFLEPUFF!(76%)

Congratulations! You have been sorted into Hufflepuff, the house of loyalty, hard working, acceptance, and fairness. You are amongst other Hufflepuffs such as: Tonks and Cedric Diggory

Additional Results:

HUFFLEPUFF! (76%)

GRYFFINDOR! (68%)

RAVENCLAW! (64%)

SLYTHERIN! (34%)

Visit: Pottermore Sorting Quiz (all possible questions)

The fascinating bit about this is that I’m evidently almost equally Hufflepuff, Griffindor and Ravenclaw - but only 34% Slytherin.  I would not have called that.

body:
I’m confused

Okay. So, I’m new to Tumblr. Like very new, and I don’t know how to use all the features yet.

That’s out of the way. The reason I’m making this post:

Forever and a day ago, I read @virgilsjourney ’s Sanders Sides Harry Potter AU head cannon formated fanfictions through chrome. There was a master post with a list of them. I truly enjoyed them and I wanted to reread them but I can’t seem to find the master post.

Could someone send me it should they stumble upon it?
